#

Sautéed Brussels Sprouts with Lemon and Parmesan

20 min
$8
150 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

AmericanItalian

Course:

Side Dish

Tags:

QuickHealthySide Dish

Description

Crispy, flavorful Brussels sprouts tossed with zesty lemon and rich Parmesan for a delicious side dish!

Ingredients

  • brussels sprouts: 1 lb
  • olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • lemon: 1, juiced
  • parmesan cheese: 1/3 cup, grated
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
